PortSystem 1.0
name		libgnome
version		2.20.1.1
revision	1
description	This is the non-gui part of the library formerly \
		known as gnome-libs.
long_description       	This is the non-gui part of the library formerly \
			known as gnome-libs. 
maintainers	rhwood openmaintainer
categories	gnome
platforms	darwin 
